“Hey my dude you have some serious drip. Drip check!”

“Want to go get some boba?” “Bet?”
“That girl that does the seagull noises has me ded💀.”
“My brother loves Megan Thee Stallion. He’s a stan.”
Sees video of a guy named Jesse buy his mom a new car. “I stan Jesse.”
“This new Olivia Rodrigo album hits different.”
“Nothing like the feeling of seeing the elote  man coming down the street. Iykyk.”
“That song lives rent free in my head.”
“He hates LeBron James so much, he lives rent free inside his head.”
“Beyonce gave us the greatest performance in music history, periodt.”
“Did you see his Instagram post about how much he loves his girlfriend? He’s such a simp.”
“I love hanging out with them. They pass the vibe check.”
“That dude yelled at the server, he doesn’t pass the vibe check.”
“That looks like fun. Can we go do that? 🥺👉👈”
Make✍️ sure ✍️ to ✍️ buy ✍️ her ✍️ flowers✍️.”
“Car sales after seeing this video📉.”
“Me when I saw those photos of Jennifer Lopez with Ben Affleck👁👄👁.”
“Today I did ✨nothing✨.”
“I have some ✨personal news✨ to share.”
“Me just trying to ignore the person screaming behind me🙂.”
“Guys I got tickets to Disneyland😭.”
“This ‘Friends: Reunion’ has me in my feels😭.”
